Moreover, when merging the beam in the LEBT and using the same RFQ, the energy of the different species should be equal. The platform of the proton ion source is + 75 kV, and so the platform voltage of the H-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
