The critical design criteria for the MEBT are summarised here:
Use as few switching magnets and/or focusing elements as possible; these switch the value between p and H-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
