				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text {ESS}}\nu {\text {SB}}$$\end{document} project starts, many of the procedures and internal safety regulations at ESS will be well established. However, the power upgrade in the linac, which will be doubled from 5 to 10 MW, will have to re-addressed. Radiation regarding neutrons generated from losses (coming from H-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
