Illustration of the extraction kicker ramping

The specifications described above will serve as input to an engineering study for kicker-magnet optimisation and construction. However, the required parameters are comparable to those of kickers already constructed for the SNS accumulator [160] and the CERN Proton Synchrotron Booster extraction region [161]. Development of the ESSνSB\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
