In the baseline pulsing scheme, the linac is pulsed at 14 Hz. As a result the accumulator will deliver a set of compressed pulses or batches to the BSY at 14 Hz, but where the batch-to-batch frequency is 1.1 kHz. Each compressed pulse or batch has a 1.2μs\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
