				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$z_2=2100\,{\text {mm}}$$\end{document}, measured from the inner edge of the collar of the horn, at the upstream end of the horn. All the elements of the frame will be made of aluminium. It is also assumed that the frame will be rigidly supported at several location on its top and bottom, including the corner points.

