In Fig. 173, the capability of the two detectors for particle identification in the crossover events using a combined analysis is shown. The identification criterion from the water Cherenkov analysis is shown, using the NLLFQμ/NLLFQe\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
