				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text {MeV}}$$\end{document}, most neutrino interactions are of the QES type. In the case of CC QES interactions, the final state contains a detectable charged lepton (muon for νμ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
